quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  40,26,"wqal fireawn lashraf qwmh: atrkwny 'aqtul mwsa, walyade rabah aldhy yazeum 'anah 'ursilah 'ilyna, fymneh mna, 'iiniy 'akhaf 'an yubaddil dinakum aladhi 'antum elyh, 'aw 'an yuzhir fi 'ard \"msr\" alfsad"
  40,27,"wqal musaa lifireawn wmlyh: 'iiniy astjrt birabiy wrbkm- 'ayuha alqwm- min kuli mstkbr ean tawhid allah wtaeth, laa yumin biawm yuhasab allah fih khlqh"
  40,28,"waqal rajul muwmin biallah min al frewn, yaktum 'iimanah mnkrana ealaa qwmh: kayf tsthlwn qatl rajul la jaram lah eindakum 'iilaa 'an yaqul rabiy allh, waqad ja'akum balbrahyn alqatet min rabikum ealaa sidq ma yqwl? fa'iina yak musaa kadhbana f'inn wbal kadhibuh eayid ealayh whdh, wa'iin yak sadqana lhqkm baed aladhi ytweeadkm bh, 'iina allah la yuafiq lalhaqu man hu mtjawz llhd, bitark alhaqu wal'iqbal ealaa albatl, kdhdhab bnsbth ma 'asraf fih 'iilaa allh"
  40,29,"ya qawm lakum alsultan alyawm zahirin fi 'ard \"msr \" ealaa reytkm min bani 'iisrayiyl wghyrhm, fman yadfae eanaa eadhab allah 'iin hll bna? qal fireawn liqawmih mjybana: ma arykm- 'ayuha alnas- min alraay walnsyht 'iilaa ma 'araa linafsi walakum slahana wswabana, wama 'adeukum 'iilaa 'iilaa tariq alhaqu walswab"
  40,30,"wqal alrajul almumin min al fireawn lifireawn wamalayih waezana wmhdhrana: 'iiniy 'akhaf ealaykum 'iin qutiltum mwsa, mithl yawm al'ahzab aladhin thzzabu ealaa anbyayhm"
  40,31,"mthl eadatan qawm nuh waead wathamud wman ja' baedihim fi alkufr waltkdhyb, ahlkhm allah bsbb dhalik. wama allah subhanah yurid zlmana llebad, fayueadhibuhum bighayr dhanb adhnbwh. taealaa allah ean alzulm walnqs elwana kbyrana"
  40,32,"wya qawm 'iiniy 'akhaf ealaykum eiqab yawm alqyamt, yawm yunadi fih bed alnaas bedana; min hwl almawqif dhlk alywm"
  40,33,"ywm tualuwn dhahbyn harbyn, ma lakum min allah min mane yamnaekum wanasir ynsrkm. wman ykhdhlh allah walam ywfqh 'iilaa rshdh, fama lah min had yahdih 'iilaa alhaqi walswab"